snippet.title: Salaar Teaser | Prabhas, Prashanth Neel, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Hombale Films, Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
THE MOST VIOLENT MEN... CALLED ONE MAN... THE MOST VIOLENT üî•
Presenting our next feature #SalaarCeaseFire to the world

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Sep 28th,2023.

SALAAR MOVIE CREDITS:
Producer : Vijay Kiragandur
Story - Screenplay - Direction : Prashanth Neel 
Salaar Star Cast - Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Hassan

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.title: Bawaal - Official Teaser | Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
National Award Winners Sajid Nadiadwala & Nitesh Tiwari bring to you Bawaal on Prime Video
Presenting the official teaser of BAWAAL 
Varun Dhawan as Ajay Dixit 
Janhvi Kapoor as Nisha 
Produced by Sajid Nadiadwala 
Directed by Nitesh Tiwari 
Co-produced by Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari 
Written by Nitesh Tiwari, Nikhil Mehrotra, Piyush Gupta, Shreyas Jain, Ashwiny Iyer Tiwari 
A Nadiadwala Grandson Entertainment and EarthSky Pictures Production  
Music on T-series

Bawaal to release on Amazon Prime Video on 21st July 2023

Teaser Audio Credits:
Music Composed, Created & Arranged by Mithoon
Lyrics: Manoj Muntashir Shukla
Singer: Arijit Singh & Mithoon
Music Production: Godswill Mergulhao & Bobby Shrivastava
Music Assts: Anugrah, Godswill Mergulhao, Eli Rodrigues & Kaushal Gohil
Guitars: Kalyan Baruah
Woodwinds: ID Rao
Violin: Jeetu Thakur
Bass: Akashdeep Gogoi
Mix & Master: Eric Pillai @ Future Sound Of Bombay
Mix Asst: Michael Edwin Pillai

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows‚Äîall with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ‚Çπ1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video‚Äôs exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ‚Çπ599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination ‚Äì Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent ‚Äì no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting‚ÄØprimevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination ‚Äì Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent ‚Äì no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting‚ÄØprimevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai | B Praak | Nawazuddin Siddiqui | Shehnaaz Gill | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents ‚ÄòYaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai‚Äô, the second single from B Praak‚Äôs debut album, ‚ÄúZohrajabeen‚Äù. Reuniting after their super hit 'Baarish Ki Jaaye', the all-star team of Nawazuddin Siddiqui, BPraak, Jaani, and Arvindr Khaira is back with yet another heart-wrenching song that explores the complexities of romance, and the pain of its absence. Experience a melancholic journey in the voice of BPraak paired with soul-stirring lyrics and composition by Jaani and a short film by Arvindr Khaira featuring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Shehnaaz Gill that embodies a bittersweet tale that can't be chased anymore, painting a picture of respectful regret.¬†Indulge your feelings in the beauty of this musical masterpiece, as it leaves you reflecting upon the significance of love and the poignancy of letting go.¬†

snippet.title: THE NUN II | OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
On September 8th, the greatest evil in the conjuring universe returns #TheNun2

New Line Cinema brings you the horror thriller ‚ÄúThe Nun II,‚Äù the next chapter in the story of ‚ÄúThe Nun,‚Äù the highest grossing entry in the juggernaut $2 billion ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù Universe.

1956 ‚Äì France. A priest is murdered. An evil is spreading. The sequel to the worldwide smash hit follows Sister Irene as she once again comes face-to-face with Valak, the demon nun.

Taissa Farmiga (‚ÄúThe Nun,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Gilded Age‚Äù) returns as Sister Irene, joined by Jonas Bloquet (‚ÄúTirailleurs,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù), Storm Reid (‚ÄúThe Last of Us,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Anna Popplewell (‚ÄúFairytale,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Chronicles of Narnia‚Äù trilogy) and Bonnie Aarons (reprising her role from ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù), surrounded by an ensemble cast of international talent.

Michael Chaves (‚ÄúThe Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It‚Äù) directs, from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing (‚ÄúEli,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Autopsy of Jane Doe‚Äù) and Akela Cooper (‚ÄúM3GAN,‚Äù ‚ÄúMalignant‚Äù),with a story by Cooper, based on characters created by James Wan & Gary Dauberman.

The Safran Company‚Äôs Peter Safran and Atomic Monster‚Äôs James Wan produce, continuing their collaboration as filmmakers on all of the previous ‚ÄúConjuring‚Äù films. ‚ÄúThe Nun II‚Äù is executive produced by Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Victoria Palmeri, Gary Dauberman, Michael Clear, Judson Scott and Michael Polaire.
Joining Chaves behind the camera are director of photography Tristan Nyby (‚ÄúThe Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Dark and the Wicked‚Äù), production designer St√©phane Cressend (‚ÄúLes Vedettes,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe French Dispatch‚Äù), editor Gregory Plotkin (2022‚Äôs ‚ÄúScream,‚Äù ‚ÄúGet Out‚Äù), visual effects producer Sophie A. Leclerc (‚ÄúFinch,‚Äù ‚ÄúLucy‚Äù) and costume designer Agn√®s B√©ziers (‚ÄúOxygen,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Breitner Commando‚Äù), with composer Marco Beltrami (2022‚Äôs ‚ÄúScream,‚Äù ‚ÄùVenom: Let There Be Carnage‚Äù) providing the score.

‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù Universe is the highest grossing horror franchise in history with $2+ billion worldwide. Globally, four of ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù Universe titles have earned more than $300 million worldwide each (‚ÄúThe Nun,‚Äù $366 million; ‚ÄúThe Conjuring 2,‚Äù $322 million; ‚ÄúThe Conjuring,‚Äù $320 million; ‚ÄúAnnabelle: Creation,‚Äù $307 million), and all seven have each grossed more than $200 million. ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù is the top-earning film in the franchise, with more than $366 million worldwide.

New Line Cinema presents an Atomic Monster / Safran Company production, ‚ÄúThe Nun II,‚Äù distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is set to open in North America on September 8, 2023 and internationally beginning 6 September, 2023.

snippet.description:
Namaste, Bajaj and Triumph are now ready with their first jointly developed bike of 400cc, the speed 400. With just Rs 2, 33,000 ex-showroom this looks amazing on paper and for first 10,000 customers there is a discount of Rs 10,000 each. Not just that, in a joint conference, Bajaj and Triumph said that the scrambler 400x will be launched soon and a cafe racer version will follow. Jhoom 2nd Last Episode 15 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Kadwani - Zara Noor Abbas - Digitally Presented by Spot-Less Skin With Ponds - 7th July 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Jhoom Digitally Presented by Spot-Less Skin With Ponds

A journey of JHOOM into the world of love, relationships, heartbreak, and sacrifice that centers around the lives of two souls who find love in a world of chaos and uncertainty that changes their lives forever. Aryaan is a young and handsome boy who holds a caring and possessive nature towards his friends. Despite having a traumatic past, Aryaan tries to smile through the worries of life and never steps back from helping his friends.

However, Aryaan's life takes an unexpected turn when he meets Maryam, a compassionate and kind-hearted woman who becomes a ray of sunshine in his life. As their relationship begin to flourish, Aryaan feels a change in himself and embraces the love that he had been deprived for so long.

Despite the significant age gap between them, Aryaan and Maryam's love for each other knows no bounds, and they embark on an unconventional journey together. Their love defies societal norms and expectations, challenging the prejudices and biases of those around them.

As their relationship progresses, their love is put to the ultimate test. Will they be able to overcome their challenges and sacrifices to stay together? Will their love stand the test of time and societal pressure? Is age just a number when it comes to love?

Written By: Hashim Nadeem
Directed By: Ali Faizan

Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: Not bad - Hero Harley Davidson X440 First Ride Experience!
snippet.description: Here‚Äôs our first ride review of the Harley Davidson x440, conceptualised and made in India for the world. With a completely new chassis and a long-stroke engine, the Harley Davidson is actually eyeing the market share of Royal Enfield which actually holds the majority in the middle-weight segment. While the performance is likeable, what‚Äôs even more interesting is the fact that it‚Äôs priced so very well at Rs 2.29 lacs (ex-showroom). Yes there are some negatives too, which we have highlighted in our first ride experience.

Amar Saxena is a businessman, and the managing director of prestigious Khaitan Fans Ltd., India. One day while leaving from a board meeting, he meets a beggar named Jagmohan, who calls him Rohit, and asks him to return home to his ailing wife, Seema. Amar denies being Rohit, but feels sorry for him and gives him some money, which Jagmohan declines to accept. Curious at his refusal, Amar offers to help. He visits the hospital and gets to meet Seema, and ends up falling in love with her. What he does not know that Jagmohan and Seema are plainclothes police officers, who have been assigned to arrest him for the murder of Ram Kumar Saxena, Amar's uncle. Using his wits, Amar manages to convince the Court that he is of unsound mind, and thus escapes being imprisoned, and ends up in an asylum. From here Amar must stock of his life, and figure out who has framed him for a murder he did not commit, and why Seema and Jagmohan were so intent to incriminate him.

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Khalasi | Aditya Gadhvi x Achint
snippet.description:
#Khalasi tells the tale of the limitless sailor who is set out to explore through the shores of Gujarat. The song speaks of his tenuous, adventurous voyage, his delightful experiences and his enthusiasm with which he takes on life while he is sailing away!

Headlining iconic music composer Achint Thakkar whose musical landscape tends to be inspired by the 70‚Äôs and aims to draw a narrative through his musical notes.  

He was joined by famous playback singer from Gujarat, Aditya Gadhvi. Known for singing in several languages and producing numerous chart hits that were singles. 

In addition to them, the song also boasts of Dhruv Visvanath, India‚Äôs premier solo percussive acoustic guitarist who also happens to be a professional singer-songwriter, and producer.  
Join them on this musical voyage.

Follow us on Instagram: Http://www.instagram.com/CokeStudioBharat

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3816 | 6 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3816: Bin Bulaye Mehman
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jetha and his team head to the police station to liberate Sundar, they are confronted by three strange beings who try to intimidate them. These people are later revealed to be Sundar and his crew, who were only playing a joke on them. Jetha inquires about Daya's return, and Sundar responds that he is unsure about her return to Gokuldham. Jetha is enraged with Sundar because he misses his wife. Champaklal calls Jetha to inquire about Sundar's whereabouts and is relieved to learn that he is safe. Sundar and his pals arrive at Gada's house and prepare to sleep, but who will sleep in the corridor? Watch the episode to see more of the amusing scenes!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3816, 6 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.

Haye Kade aa mohali hunde kade aa kasol ni 
Mitran da rehnda ae hye garm mahol ni 
Haye Kade aa mohali hunde kade aa kasol ni 
Mitran da rehnda ae hye garm mahol ni
Road ute jyada tar rehnde gadd khane 
Tenu pta pinda alle fatte chak dinde janne
Tu ta jannndi ae sara jandi ae sara 
Rehnda top ute para top ute para 
Kanch khaan tayi jande khan tayi jande 
Kithe dekh de ne khara dekh de ne khara 

Jado bhang wali bhajjdi trip goriye 
Tuvi wala vicho kad di clip goriye 
Ah patla ja lakk tadvake na tu behji
Heel patli aa hoje na slip goriye 

Tera nashyayi da ni hassa marda 
Kal kal kehndi jo dilasa maarda 
Baah de ute jehda ni tu tatto khidvaya 
Bajje dil ute jive koi gandasa marda 

Eh na samji ke daru nal dakke paye ne 
Dakke baach kam walle  fatte chake paye ne 
Bhave ajj to hi vehle rehn lag jayiye ni 
Langhu tohr nal ene ku ta rakhe paye ne 
 
Suit wakhiyan to tang tere tang karde 
Yaar tere kolo pyar di aa mang karde asi 
Maade dheede kam nu na hath paya kde 
Jihnu paya phir bs pura taang karde 

Ajj milonge na pakka jado kehndi ae ni tu 
Sach dssa jaan kadh laindi ae ni tu 
Ik vaari atma shreer chd di ni 
Mere kol je di hoke jado behndi ae ni tu 

Akh khdi hundi km tait hunda ae 
Sade nal kalla kalla bnda gahint hunda ae 
Dine billo shokiya jya  rakhye ni geda 
Per athne je dera ta haye flat hunda ae 
 
Bule luttlo jawani phir mud ke ni auni 
4 din ni paronii puri reej na jyoni 
Kam vi aa karo nale lao vi swaad 
Hath apne aa hunda life kive di bnauni 

Sajj dajj puri neri thaal rakhi di 
Vairiye de seene agg baal rakhi di 
Yara layi ta moohon bas love you nikle ni 
Dallya layi mooh de ute gaal rakhi di 

Pyare jattan de puttan layi lalkare hunde aa
Athne je painde ni khlare hunde aa
Hunda ni swaal paida karne koi naah 
Ethe peeen ni ready baithe sare hunde aa
Jado rall behnde koi na koi hundi aa kalol ni 

Kade aa mohali hunde kade aa kasol ni 
Mittran da rehnda ae haye garm mahol ni 
Road ute jyada tar rehnde gadd khane 
Tenu pta pinda alle fatte chak dinde janne

To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Salaar Teaser Reaction | Prabhas, Prashanth Neel, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Hombale Films
snippet.description:
#Salaar #Prabhas #HombaleFilms
 From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Sep 28th,2023.

SALAAR MOVIE CREDITS:
Producer : Vijay Kiragandur
Story - Screenplay - Direction : Prashanth Neel 
Salaar Star Cast - Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Hassan
DOP : Bhuvan Gowda
Production Designer : Shivakumar - T L Venkatachalapathi 
Music : Ravi Basrur
Stunts : Anbarivu 
Costume Designer : Thota Vijay Bhaskar 
Executive Producers : KV Rama Rao - Karthik 
Editor : Ujwal Kulkarni 
Dialogues : Sandeep Reddy Bandla - Hanuman Chaudhary - DR Suri 
VFX Supervisor : Raghav Tamma Reddy 
Lyricist : Krishna Kanth 
 
Direction Team:
AARUN THEVAR - KIRTAN NADAGOUDA
DHODL PRAKASH (EMM) - BHARGAV N (ERY) - NANDA KISHORE ABBURU - VEDHA KALAVAKURI - CHALLAGULLA NANI - HARISH MADALA - SREERAM VADLAMANI - MURALI MUDDENAHALLY
GOWRA CHANDRABABL NAIDU - AKASH THARGAAR - LIKHITH RAGHUVEER S- RAM REDDY MARELLA - SUPREME KRANTHI SURYA - FARMAN ULLA

snippet.title: Sandeep Bhaiya | New Web Series | EP 01 | Mulyankan
snippet.description:
Jab sapno ke last attempt mein failure milta hai tab koi Plan B kaam nahi aata, dekhiye ek aise student ki kahani jisne haar naa maan kar ALC tak ka safar tay kiya. 

Rate us on IMDb: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt28227737/

1 out of every 3 selections* in UPSC CSE 2022 is from Unacademy.

Embark on your path to becoming an IAS/IPS officer with Unacademy. Learn and be mentored by Top Educators like Mrunal Patel, Avadh Ojha, Sudarshan Gurjar, Sidharth Arora, Pratik Nayak, and many more.  

üéØTake a Free Online Class: https://unacademy.onelink.me/M2BR/zyo849op
üéØBook a visit at Unacademy Delhi Centre: https://unacademy.onelink.me/M2BR/rx385s4a
üéØIOS: https://unacademy.onelink.me/081J/a61
üéØAndroid: https://unacademy.onelink.me/081J/40a

*Includes all learners associated with Unacademy

Umeed tootne pe zindagi bhi naaraz hoti hai par hote hain kuch log jinhe haar manzoor nahi! Sandeep Bhaiya is a character who never accepted failure and always motivated others to achieve their goals too. This show revolves around his journey from being a UPSC student to becoming a civil servant.

Episode 2 Streaming Now: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t7roMhZg6zg

snippet.title: CID MOOSA | 20 Years Special Mashup
snippet.description:
20 Years of C.I.D MOOSA

C.I.D Moosa is a 2003 Indian Malayalam-language action comedy thriller film directed by Johny Antony, written by Udaykrishna‚ÄìSibi K. Thomas duo, and co-produced by Dileep. It stars Dileep in the title role of a private detective, and also features Bhavana, Murali, Ashish Vidyarthi (in his Malayalam debut), Harisree Ashokan, Cochin Haneefa, Jagathy Sreekumar, Captain Raju, Oduvil Unnikrishnan, and Salim Kumar. In the film, C.I.D Moosa, a private detective, faces many challenges while solving various cases. His only rival is his own brother-in-law, Peethambaran, who is a police officer.

The film was released on 4 July 2003. It was a box office success, becoming the second highest-grossing Malayalam film of the year, behind Balettan. The film is known for its slapstick comedy and has developed a cult following.
